<item>
            <title>[LU-480] Test failure on test suite sanityn: LBUG/LASSERT detected</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-480</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for yujian &amp;lt;yujian@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/8771913e-a451-11e0-b786-52540025f9af&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/8771913e-a451-11e0-b786-52540025f9af&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_36 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;LBUG/LASSERT detected&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description>
